EURICA Time-walk correction
by Byul Moon.
Jun. 15. 2018.

For beta-delayed analysis
1. run EURICA_1.cc : make TWhist.root file sotring E vs. T 2-D histograms for each channel.
2. run EURICA_2.cc : correct time-walk by TWhist.root for every channels.
3. run EURICA_3.cc : get 4sigma cut conditions after the time-walk correction.

For isomer analysis
1. run EURICA_ISO_1.cc : make TWhist_ISO.root file sotring E vs. T 2-D histograms for each channel.
2. run EURICA_ISO_2.cc : correct time-walk by TWhist.root for every channels.
3. run EURICA_ISO_3.cc : get 4sigma cut conditions after the time-walk correction.
